ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectNo. 141 - (New Brunswick) Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER N° 141 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the province of NEW BRUNSWICK with respect to the STORM that affected the Counties of Gloucester, Kent, Northumberland and Westmoreland from December 20 to December 22, 2010.
